ck; ocean is water. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec17b7499c1187c9fa951ff69bc2fa097fe9fa3a","tid":653264,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"年年都有好多抽新股搵大錢機會，小米可以係一個機會，亦可以係一個陷阱，有閒錢咪博下囉，冇嘅就唔好抽喇，玩其他穩穩陣陣賺好過"},{"pid":"92703f194250dbc0221d73c6718f7ae10f827abb","tid":653264,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1080280d2c685204f30a6ad7a68a1c1e2c58e07","tid":653264,"uid":99307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92703f194250dbc0221d73c6718f7ae10f827abb","tid":653264,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"百幾億美金係話,三星過去有7億純利時所擁有市值<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5076ef6ded9564f9e758ea2b2b28002916aa42","tid":653264,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"367ef7a4636b2b7582b0e4a8596e7b92bfef280b","tid":653264,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報：Mother is a girl; mountain is rock; ocean is water. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T20:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寫比d唔識中文的鬼佬睇<br />\n中國d衰野除咗侵侵同隊crew同東亞國家<br />\n其他西人係唔知具體情況可以有幾惡劣<br />\n<br />\n淨係講整個中國極醜惡英文專版都咪話唔精彩，頭條日本dom阿伯撞電車登頭版，下面澳洲偷菜大媽團，角落黎講香港聯和墟小販被打，d鬼佬一定個個變唔撚係話樹熊，因為d害人招式已經超出佢地想像"},{"pid":"fdbf541e64e191435a0c193c702c392db7e207b7","tid":653264,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T20:28:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾小米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e0c27f056ea14e3edba7536d383474e1c18036","tid":653264,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T20:59:45